  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the grief or resentment that sits alongside the inherited money pattern. The script moves toward forgiveness — not forgetting what happened, but releasing the weight of carrying it."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
          { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works" } }], "text": "how EFT tapping works" },
          { "type": "text", "text": " first." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "The practice" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Karate chop" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I carry grief about what the women before me didn't have, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though it feels hard to forgive what was passed on, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though their pain became my pattern, I am open to releasing it with love." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tapping round" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " They didn't have what I have." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " They carried fear I was handed without asking for it." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I grieve what they went through." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " And I resent that it became my inheritance." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " It was hard. It was unfair. It was real." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I have been carrying something that isn't mine to keep carrying." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm ready to put it down with love." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I honour what they survived." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " They did what they could with what they had." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " The fear was a survival response, not a sentence." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I forgive them for passing on what they hadn't yet released." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I release this on their behalf as well as mine." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Their struggle is honoured. It doesn't need to live in me to be real." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I carry their strength, not their fear." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I get to thrive in ways they couldn't." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I build a new line from here." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times." }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adapted from Day 12 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Forgive ancestors' financial pain.\" The tapping framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
